description: Lists analysis templates that the caller owns.

parameters.name: membershipIdentifier
parameters.description: The identifier for a membership resource.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token that's used to fetch the next set of results.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the analysis template.

nested_items.name: createTime
nested_items.description: The time that the analysis template summary was created.

nested_items.name: id
nested_items.description: The identifier of the analysis template.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the analysis template.

nested_items.name: updateTime
nested_items.description: The time that the analysis template summary was last updated.

nested_items.name: membershipArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the member who created the analysis template.

nested_items.name: membershipId
nested_items.description: The identifier for a membership resource.

nested_items.name: collaborationArn
nested_items.description: The unique ARN for the analysis template summary's associated collaboration.

nested_items.name: collaborationId
nested_items.description: A unique identifier for the collaboration that the analysis template summary belongs to. Currently accepts collaboration ID.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The description of the analysis template.
